title: (Tues Early Bird) Scuba Steve's Huge Fear + We Play Never Gonna Get it + Mailbag: Setting Up Friend With Husband's Identical Twin
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) Scuba Steve's Huge Fear + We Play Never Gonna Get it + Mailbag: Setting Up Friend With Husband's Identical Twin
description:
Scuba Steve shares what his biggest fear is, especially when he's traveling, and why. We play Never Gonna Get It with a listener and ask them recent survey questions that they have to answer correctly. Bobby opens the mailbag and helps a listener who says her friend wants to set her up with her husband's identical time, but she doesn't find the twin attractive. We help her figure out how she should handle the situation.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
